{
  "stem": "13251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was all, you know, very interesting and-- but what was really the intense thing that happened to me that blew my mind is while I was just sitting there, somebody tapped me on the shoulder and said-- this-- this lady said to me, hi, would you be interested-- I'd like you to meet this gentleman who was responsible for you coming to England.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought what kind of-- you know, I never heard of anybody responsible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I assumed all these years that-- that-- there was, like, a Rabbi or Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schonfeld, very well known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he was organizing Jewish organizations and government, you know, together with a government, they-- they brought many children out from Europe after the wars-- concentration survivors-- concentration camp survivors.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he also, I found out, before the war did that, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I assumed that's the way I came to England is through the efforts of Jewish organizations and the British government, and I was always grateful for that, of course.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he said individual, I thought, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't believe it, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, in England everybody's polite, so I went along with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I went along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she took me over-- and she took me over to this older guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And hey, this is Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nicholas Winton, is his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and he says hi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, what's your name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we said, Pinkasovic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So without any-- he right away went to his file, and he-- he opened up-- I guess it was like alphabetical order, and I see my name in there, Pinkasovic.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I saw that, I mean, I can't tell you how I felt, I mean, the intensity of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had goosebumps all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
